    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required Gradation 2 level for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all operating points with NIH deviation within experimental uncertainty. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under the defined COU.",
